## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7b96f-217">以下示例创建排序一份披萨语音识别的语法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7b96f-217">The following example creates a speech recognition grammar for ordering a pizza.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7b96f-218">它与可选的打开的短语后, 跟一到四个浇头启动，并以单词"pizza"将关闭。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7b96f-218">It starts with an optional, opening phrase, followed by one to four toppings, and closes with the word "pizza".</span></span>  
  
