 <span data-ttu-id="7b96f-453"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 支持从以下类转换：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7b96f-453"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> supports conversions from the following classes:</span></span>  
  
