 <span data-ttu-id="7b96f-454">此方法接受为上面列出的对象`builder`参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7b96f-454">This method accepts the objects listed above for the `builder` parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7b96f-455">有关详细信息，请参阅<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A>运算符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7b96f-455">For more information, see the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> operators.</span></span>  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
